data.description: Welcome to 8562 W West Knoll Dr 10, a remarkable property that carries with it a touch of musical legacy. This isn’t just any home; it’s the very place connected to the iconic song “Midnight Train to Georgia,” the standard hit song by Gladys Knight and the pips. Steeped in artistic inspiration, this condo holds a unique connection to the world of music.     What sets this property apart even further is the seller's exceptional foresight—a 2.75% interest mortgage rate that can be assumed by the buyer. This presents a rare financial advantage, enhancing the appeal of this exquisite home.    Nestled within a Mediterranean complex, this exquisite West Hollywood pied-à-terre offers a lifestyle that’s nothing short of exceptional. Immerse yourself in the opulence of architectural elegance, potentially offered fully furnished in the style of Architectural Digest. From the moment you step through the gated European courtyard, you’ll be enveloped in a world of luxury.     This residence has been curated with the finest finishes and exquisite wallpapers, all handpicked by designers for an unparalleled sense of refinement. High ceilings create an airy ambiance, while sunlight cascades through French doors, beckoning you to lush balconies that bring the outdoors in. Imagine indulging in the warmth of a cozy fireplace, or entertaining under the stars on your private rooftop deck.     The charming kitchen is a culinary haven, and the convenience of laundry in unit adds a touch of practicality to luxury living. With a private two-car security garage offering direct entry, your peace of mind is paramount.     Location couldn’t be more prime – mere steps from the Sunset Strip, Sunset Plaza, and West Hollywood’s vibrant dining and entertainment scene. Nestled adjacent to the prestige of Beverly Hills, you’re at the crossroads of style, culture, and luxury in this perfect pied-à-terre.     Unlock a lifestyle that combines musical heritage, architectural opulence, and the very best of West Hollywood living. Don’t miss the opportunity to call 8562 W West Knoll Dr 10 your own.
